Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想早點告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,話說朏君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你有想過貓的名字嗎
